							아이디 저장
						</span>
					</div>
					<!--버튼2개박스-->
					<div class="btnWrap">
						<ul>
							<li class="joinBtn"><a href="/IGOProject/member/regist" class="on">회원가입</a></li>
							<li class="joinBtn joinBtn2"><a href="idpw.jsp">ID/PW 찾기</a></li>
